title: Minutemen Scans Week of 05.28.09 (complete edition)
description:
Minutemen Scans Week of 05.20.09 (complete edition)

This is the first of a few "catch-up" MM torrent packs.  There should be one every few days until we're current.  After that, we'll be switching to a new scheme where MM 0-day comics will be contained in a general 0-day pack and MM non-0-day books will be put into their own torrent pack so you can grab the newest back issues.

Sorry for the delay and please seed so I can up more packs.
